flowchart TD
    A[Candidate sends CV or application form] --> B[HR downloads CV]
    B --> C[HR updates tracking spreadsheet]
    C --> D[HR screens candidate manually]
    D --> E{Pass screening?}

    E -- No --> F[HR sends rejection manually]
    E -- Yes --> G[HR contacts candidate]
    G --> H[HR schedules interview by chat or email]
    H --> I[Interviewer reviews CV]
    I --> J[Interview is conducted]
    J --> K[Interviewer sends feedback by chat or email]
    K --> L[HR updates candidate status manually]
    L --> M[Hiring manager reviews selected candidates]
    M --> N[HR sends final result]